# Target modern evergreen browsers + Safari 15+
# For personal blog/portfolio with modern CSS features

# Modern browsers (auto-update)
last 2 Chrome versions
last 2 Firefox versions
last 2 Edge versions

# Safari (including iOS)
Safari >= 15
iOS >= 15

# Exclude dead browsers
not dead
not IE 11
not op_mini all

# Market share threshold
> 0.5% in US
